      "text": "I never knew, you know, as a kid, 'La Donna E Mobile.' And he was telling us exactly the story of the opera, about his life, about his daughter.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he even made jokes all the time that he will give us his daughter.",
