      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She's in hiding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We never ask where, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody would say, my daughter's in hiding, because you don't even tell it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he had, himself, this philosophy of exactly the same as [? 'El ?] [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
