      "text": "He was a jester, the singer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The daughter that he gives to people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was in our camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you have these kind of daily occurrence that you don't even think-- for a while, I did not think.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was in the night, in the opera, 'La Donna E Mobile.' I knew the whole 'La Donna E Mobile,' that's where it's coming.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it remind me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
